    "title": "The Maverick",
    "start": "2021-09-17T02:00:00.000Z",
    "end": "2021-09-17T05:00:00.000Z",
    "location": "",
    "description": "Our contact is Abby Tracey.\n\n$500\n\n\nThe stage is right by the front door - gotta load in through the main entrance. It's\u00a0 roughly a right-triangle - It's about 17 feet across the front - each of the sides go back 13 feet.\u00a0 Bigger than Frisco and better laid out.\n\nWe have to bring our own sound.\u00a0 All their plugs are on the left side of stage (from audience view) but there were a lot of them\n\nThey have stage lights - but some more would be better.\u00a0\u00a0\n\nMy rough guess is that they can seat about 200-250 people - with standing room back by games and pool tables.\n\n\nThey had a little place by the door to store excess equipment - they said no one ever sits there."
